About Blissfully
Blissfully is humanizing and simplifying IT.

 

Leadership Team
Blissfully is founded by repeat technology entrepreneurs, experienced in building great teams, and engineering great products, financings, and outcomes.





 
Ariel Diaz
Founder and CEO
Ariel is originally from Miami, FL, studied engineering and business at Dartmouth, worked and played semi-pro soccer in Germany, spent nearly a decade in Boston, and now lives in New York City.





 



 



 



 



 



 






 
Aaron White
Founder and CTO
Aaron has spent two decades leading product & technology development, as well as investing & and advising early stage technology startups.





 



 



 



 



 


 

Investors
Blissfully is backed by Founder Collective and a group of experienced entrepreneurs. 
View more details at Angel List.

 










