Stop worrying about “Shadow IT”.
Start leveraging your entire organization’s intelligence, and stop fighting shadow IT. Get an instant IT security audit to see where company data is going, identify potential risks, and ensure vendors meet your security policies.

 
Get proactive value, in your inbox.
Get alerts whenever anyone in your organization signs up for a new SaaS product, reminders for upcoming renewals, weekly and monthly summaries to stay on top of everything, and other insights, delivered automatically.

 


