Marketing Intern at Blissfully
New York City · Internship






Blissfully is humanizing, simplifying and automating IT management for our customers.


Read More




Blissfully is humanizing, simplifying and automating IT management for our customers.
Our beach-head product automatically identifies all SaaS products an organization uses and pays for, delivering deeper insights automatically, helping save money, reduce security risks, and improve productivity.
Blissfully is founded by repeat technology entrepreneurs, experienced in building great teams, and engineering great products, financings, and outcomes.













Applied





Apply to Blissfully







Add a message to Blissfully



Apply




















Job Description



We're looking for a marketing intern through September 2017. 
We're building amazing tools to help companies manage the explosion in SaaS tools they're using, and poised to ride the massive momentum as companies increasingly move to the cloud. Our first product automatically detects all the SaaS tools a company is using, creating great insights and opportunities for companies to save money and reduce security risks. The role will help support tests and experiments around multiple growth channels.
Ideal background + Requirements
- Strong work ethic, creativity, and ability to work independently
- You should be deeply analytical, make data driven decisions, and hopefully be proficient in a variety of analytics platforms
- You should be a strong copywriter, and be able to do and manage content marketing
Bonus experience: 
- Experience growing a B2B software company.
- Experience across a broad set of marketing efforts, including email marketing, content marketing, SEO, and paid ads.
Why Join
You'll get in on the ground floor in super interesting business, working with experienced founders, touching many parts of the business.



Skills

Data Analysis, SEO/SEM, Copywriting, Content Marketing, B2B Marketing, Analtyics

